sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant A as Coding Agent
    participant AD as Connect Adapter
    participant C as Connect Core
    participant CS as ContractSpec Artifacts
    participant S as Studio (optional)

    U->>A: Request change
    A->>AD: Proposed /plan
    AD->>C: Normalize plan action
    C->>CS: Resolve contracts, manifests, policy
    C->>C: Build ContextPack
    C->>C: Compile and verify PlanPacket
    C-->>AD: plan verdict
    AD-->>A: Approved / revise / review / deny

    A->>AD: Proposed edit or command
    AD->>C: Normalize mutating action
    C->>CS: Resolve impacted contracts/surfaces
    C->>C: Run verifier pipeline
    C->>C: Write audit event
    alt require_review
        C->>S: Emit review packet
        S-->>C: Review item ref
    end
    C-->>AD: PatchVerdict
    AD-->>A: permit / rewrite / require_review / deny
